---
// Marco Ferrante Studio — mockup fotografo/videografo
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Marco Ferrante Studio — Fotografia & Video</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,700;1,400&family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --black: #080808;
      --dark: #111111;
      --card: #1a1a1a;
      --gold: #c9a84c;
      --gold-light: #e8cc7a;
      --white: #f5f2ed;
      --muted: rgba(245,242,237,0.5);
      --serif: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif;
      --sans: 'Space Grotesk', system-ui, sans-serif;
    }

    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body { background: var(--black); color: var(--white); font-family: var(--sans); font-weight: 300; overflow-x: hidden; }

    /* BACK BTN */
    .back-btn {
      position: fixed; bottom: 2rem; left: 1.5rem; z-index: 999;
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
      background: rgba(8,8,8,0.85); backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
      color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; font-family: var(--sans);
      font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 0.05em; padding: 0.55rem 1rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); border-radius: 2rem;
      transition: all 0.2s;
    }
    .back-btn:hover { color: var(--white); border-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); }

    /* NAV */
    nav {
      position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100;
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 1.5rem 3rem; background: transparent;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }
    nav.scrolled { background: rgba(8,8,8,0.9); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); }
    .nav-logo {
      font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--white);
      letter-spacing: 0.05em; text-decoration: none;
    }
    .nav-logo span { color: var(--gold); }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 2.5rem; list-style: none; }
    .nav-links a {
      color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      transition: color 0.2s;
    }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--white); }

    /* HERO */
    .hero {
      position: relative; height: 100vh; display: flex;
      align-items: flex-end; overflow: hidden;
    }
    .hero-bg {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background-image: url('/images/portfolio/foto-hero.jpg');
      background-size: cover; background-position: center;
      transform: scale(1.05);
      animation: slowzoom 12s ease-out forwards;
    }
    @keyframes slowzoom { to { transform: scale(1); } }
    .hero-overlay {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(8,8,8,0.95) 0%, rgba(8,8,8,0.4) 50%, rgba(8,8,8,0.2) 100%);
    }
    .hero-content {
      position: relative; z-index: 2;
      padding: 0 4rem 5rem;
      max-width: 900px;
    }
    .hero-eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--gold); font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em;
      text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .hero-eyebrow::before {
      content: ''; display: block; width: 2.5rem; height: 1px;
      background: var(--gold);
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 8vw, 7rem);
      font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.0; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }
    .hero h1 em { color: var(--gold); font-style: italic; }
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: 0.85rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    .hero-cta {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 1rem;
      background: var(--gold); color: var(--black);
      text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 1rem 2rem; transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .hero-cta:hover { background: var(--gold-light); }
    .hero-scroll {
      position: absolute; right: 3rem; bottom: 3rem;
      display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
      color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em;
      text-transform: uppercase; z-index: 2;
    }
    .hero-scroll::after {
      content: ''; display: block; width: 1px; height: 3rem;
      background: var(--gold); animation: scrollline 2s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
    @keyframes scrollline { 0%,100%{opacity:0.3;transform:scaleY(0.5)} 50%{opacity:1;transform:scaleY(1)} }

    /* STATS BAR */
    .stats-bar {
      background: var(--card); border-top: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
      display: flex; justify-content: center;
    }
    .stats-inner {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      max-width: 900px; width: 100%;
    }
    .stat {
      padding: 2rem 2.5rem; text-align: center;
      border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }
    .stat:last-child { border-right: none; }
    .stat-num {
      font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 2.4rem; color: var(--gold);
      line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
    }
    .stat-label { font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); }

    /* SECTION HEADER */
    .section-header {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
    }
    .section-tag {
      font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold);
    }
    .section-header::after {
      content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    }

    /* GALLERY */
    .gallery-section { padding: 6rem 3rem; }
    .gallery-intro { max-width: 600px; margin-bottom: 4rem; }
    .gallery-intro h2 {
      font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(2rem,4vw,3.5rem);
      font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .gallery-intro p { color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.8; }

    .gallery-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      grid-template-rows: auto auto;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .gallery-item {
      overflow: hidden; position: relative;
      background: var(--card);
    }
    .gallery-item.large { grid-column: span 2; grid-row: span 2; }
    .gallery-item img {
      width: 100%; height: 100%; min-height: 280px;
      object-fit: cover; display: block;
      transition: transform 0.6s ease;
    }
    .gallery-item:hover img { transform: scale(1.04); }
    .gallery-item .overlay {
      position: absolute; inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to top, rgba(8,8,8,0.7) 0%, transparent 60%);
      opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.3s;
      display: flex; align-items: flex-end;
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    .gallery-item:hover .overlay { opacity: 1; }
    .gallery-item .overlay span {
      font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 0.1em;
      text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--white);
    }

    /* SERVICES */
    .services-section { padding: 5rem 3rem; background: var(--dark); }
    .services-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 1px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }
    .service-card {
      background: var(--dark); padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      transition: background 0.3s;
    }
    .service-card:hover { background: var(--card); }
    .service-icon {
      font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }
    .service-card h3 {
      font-family: var(--serif); font-size: 1.3rem; font-weight: 400;
      margin-bottom: 0.8rem; color: var(--white);
    }
    .service-card p {
      font-size: 0.85rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--muted);
    }
    .service-price {
      margin-top: 1.5rem; font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    /* ABOUT */
    .about-section { padding: 7rem 3rem; }
    .about-grid {
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 5rem; align-items: center;
    }
    .about-image-wrap {
      position: relative;
    }
    .about-image-wrap::before {
      content: ''; position: absolute;
      top: -1.5rem; left: -1.5rem; right: 1.5rem; bottom: 1.5rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.3);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .about-image-wrap img {
      width: 100%; display: block;
      object-fit: cover; aspect-ratio: 3/4;
      filter: grayscale(20%);
    }
    .about-content { padding-right: 2rem; }
    .about-content .label {
      font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold); margin-bottom: 1rem; display: block;
    }
    .about-content h2 {
      font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(2rem,3.5vw,3rem);
      font-weight: 400; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .about-content p {
      color: var(--muted); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.9;
      margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }
    .about-awards {
      margin-top: 2.5rem; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem;
    }
    .award-item {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.2rem;
      padding-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    }
    .award-year { font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--gold); width: 3rem; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .award-name { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--white); }
    .award-org { font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); }

    /* CTA */
    .cta-section {
      padding: 7rem 3rem; text-align: center;
      background: var(--dark);
      background-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 100%, rgba(201,168,76,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
    }
    .cta-section .label {
      font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--gold); display: block; margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .cta-section h2 {
      font-family: var(--serif); font-size: clamp(2rem,5vw,4rem);
      font-weight: 400; margin-bottom: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.2;
    }
    .cta-section p {
      color: var(--muted); font-size: 1rem; max-width: 480px;
      margin: 0 auto 3rem; line-height: 1.8;
    }
    .cta-btns { display: flex; gap: 1rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .btn-primary {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem;
      background: var(--gold); color: var(--black);
      text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 500;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 1rem 2.5rem; transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--gold-light); }
    .btn-outline {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.6rem;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2); color: var(--white);
      text-decoration: none; font-size: 0.8rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 1rem 2.5rem; transition: border-color 0.2s;
    }
    .btn-outline:hover { border-color: var(--gold); color: var(--gold); }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      nav { padding: 1rem 1.5rem; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .hero-content { padding: 0 1.5rem 4rem; }
      .hero-scroll { display: none; }
      .stats-inner { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
      .gallery-section, .services-section, .about-section, .cta-section { padding-left: 1.5rem; padding-right: 1.5rem; }
      .gallery-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .gallery-item.large { grid-column: span 1; grid-row: span 1; }
      .services-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
      .about-content { padding-right: 0; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <a href="/dev/portfolio" class="back-btn">← Portfolio</a>

  <nav id="nav">
    <a href="#" class="nav-logo">Marco Ferrante<span>.</span></a>
    <ul class="nav-links">
      <li><a href="#gallery">Lavori</a></li>
      <li><a href="#servizi">Servizi</a></li>
      <li><a href="#about">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contatti">Contatto</a></li>
    </ul>
  </nav>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <div class="hero-eyebrow">Fotografia &amp; Cinema — Milano</div>
      <h1>Marco<br /><em>Ferrante</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">Studio fotografico &amp; video production</p>
      <a href="#gallery" class="hero-cta">Esplora il lavoro →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-scroll">Scroll</div>
  </section>

  <div class="stats-bar">
    <div class="stats-inner">
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-num">340+</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Servizi completati</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-num">12</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Anni di attività</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-num">8</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Premi nazionali</div>
      </div>
      <div class="stat">
        <div class="stat-num">3</div>
        <div class="stat-label">Paesi coperti</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="gallery-section" id="gallery">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-tag">Portfolio</span>
    </div>
    <div class="gallery-intro">
      <h2>Ogni immagine racconta una <em>storia</em></h2>
      <p>Dal matrimonio al ritratto corporate, dall'architettura alla campagna pubblicitaria. Ogni progetto nasce da un'ascolto attento e si conclude con immagini che durano nel tempo.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="gallery-grid">
      <div class="gallery-item large">
        <img src="/images/portfolio/foto-hero.jpg" alt="Studio fotografico" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="overlay"><span>Studio &amp; Ritratto</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="gallery-item">
        <img src="/images/portfolio/foto-wedding.jpg" alt="Matrimoni" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="overlay"><span>Matrimoni</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="gallery-item">
        <img src="/images/portfolio/foto-corporate.jpg" alt="Corporate" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="overlay"><span>Corporate</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="gallery-item">
        <img src="/images/portfolio/foto-landscape.jpg" alt="Paesaggio" loading="lazy" />
        <div class="overlay"><span>Reportage</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="services-section" id="servizi">
    <div class="section-header">
      <span class="section-tag">Servizi</span>
    </div>
    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">💍</div>
        <h3>Matrimoni</h3>
        <p>Racconto completo del giorno, dal preparativi alla festa. Reportage naturale e ritratti formali.</p>
        <div class="service-price">da 2.400 €</div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">👤</div>
        <h3>Ritratti</h3>
        <p>Headshot professionali, book personali e ritratti artistici in studio o in location scelta.</p>
        <div class="service-price">da 380 €</div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">🏢</div>
        <h3>Corporate</h3>
        <p>Fotografia istituzionale, team, eventi aziendali. Licenza commerciale inclusa.</p>
        <div class="service-price">da 750 €</div>
      </div>
      <div class="service-card">
        <div class="service-icon">🎬</div>
        <h3>Video</h3>
        <p>Spot pubblicitari, company profile, documentari brevi. Montaggio professionale incluso.</p>
        <div class="service-price">da 1.800 €</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-section" id="about">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-image-wrap">
        <img src="/images/portfolio/foto-about.jpg" alt="Marco Ferrante fotografo" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="about-content">
        <span class="label">Chi sono</span>
        <h2>Vent'anni di occhio, un'ora per capire la tua storia</h2>
        <p>Fotografo professionista dal 2005, mi sono formato a Milano e New York prima di tornare a costruire il mio studio. Il mio approccio è documentaristico: osservo, aspetto il momento giusto e scatto.</p>
        <p>Lavoro con brand, agenzie e privati che vogliono immagini con personalità. Non fotografie qualunque, ma immagini che portano una firma riconoscibile.</p>
        <div class="about-awards">
          <div class="award-item">
            <div class="award-year">2024</div>
            <div>
              <div class="award-name">Best Wedding Photography</div>
              <div class="award-org">Italian Wedding Awards</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="award-item">
            <div class="award-year">2022</div>
            <div>
              <div class="award-name">Commercial Photographer of the Year</div>
              <div class="award-org">FotoMedia Italia</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="award-item">
            <div class="award-year">2019</div>
            <div>
              <div class="award-name">Finalista — Portrait Category</div>
              <div class="award-org">Sony World Photography Awards</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section" id="contatti">
    <span class="label">Parliamo del tuo progetto</span>
    <h2>Hai un'idea in mente?<br /><em>Raccontamela.</em></h2>
    <p>Rispondo entro 24 ore. Per i matrimoni, consiglio di contattarmi almeno 6 mesi prima della data.</p>
    <div class="cta-btns">
      <a href="mailto:marco@ferrante.studio" class="btn-primary">Scrivimi →</a>
      <a href="tel:+393401234567" class="btn-outline">Chiamami</a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script>
    const nav = document.getElementById('nav');
    window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
      nav.classList.toggle('scrolled', window.scrollY > 80);
    });
  </script>
</body>
</html>
